title: Nicki Minaj Announced Her Pregnancy On Instagram
text:
IN Celebrities ON 05 Feb, 2017 Nicki Minaj Announced Her Pregnancy On Instagram Share on twitter Follow Us On 
American rapper, singer, and songwriter Nicki Minaj just announced her pregnancy on Instagram and a lot of people are shocked, precisely 375,732 people (and counting). This news came after Beyoncé formally announced that she is pregnant on the same platform. 
Whether this is a true revelation or just a sarcastic tease is something we will let you decide. 
Can pictures lie? Who knows! Nicki Minaj Announced Her Pregnancy On Instagram 754 396
